@page "/about-us"

<PageTitle>About Gotorz</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5 text-center">
    <!-- Section Headline -->
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #f8b500;">Gotorz</h2>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4">Get to Know Us Better</h4>

    <!-- White Content Box -->
    <div class="mx-auto p-4 text-start"
         style="
             background-color: white;
             border-radius: 5px;
             border: 1px solid lightgrey;
             box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
             max-width: 1000px;
             line-height: 1.8;
         ">

        <!-- Our Story -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold">Our Story</h5>
        <p>
            Our journey started in 2017 — a modest beginning on a Facebook page with a mission to make travel easier, more accessible, and more affordable.
            We aimed to make the joy of travel possible even for those who had never left their country before.
        </p>
        <p>
            It wasn’t long before our unique offers gained popularity in the region. We received rave feedback for our professionalism, user-friendly service,
            and a booking process that was simpler than anything our customers had experienced.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our team worked hard to create beautiful travel memories for thousands of clients — exceeding their expectations, handling all logistics, and delivering unforgettable experiences.
        </p>

        <!-- Gotorz Philosophy -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">What Gotorz Is All About</h5>
        <p>
            We believe that travel should be joyful. That there’s happiness in exploring the unknown — and we want to share that joy with as many people as possible.
        </p>
        <p>
            From hidden villages in Bosnia to snowy mountains in Switzerland, we’ve guided thousands of people through adventures they never thought possible.
        </p>
        <p>
            Gotorz was built on the love of travel, nature, simplicity, and good vibes. We speak your language, we understand your dreams,
            and we work hard to match you with the perfect destination.
        </p>

        <!-- The Future -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">The Future</h5>
        <p>
            In 2022, Gotorz officially became a licensed tourism company — transitioning to a global brand with a growing reach.
            Our website and booking platform continue to evolve, now offering faster service, clearer pricing, and an easier interface.
        </p>
        <p>
            Behind the scenes, we’re powered by modern tech and passionate people. We’re here to help you choose the perfect destination,
            book it in minutes, and enjoy every moment of the journey.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4">
            <em>This is our story — written by us, and continued by you.</em><br />
            <strong>Come travel with us. Be part of the journey.</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

